==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ovaliform
<hw>O*val"i*form</hw> <pr>(⟦osl⟧`v⟦acr⟧l"⟦icr⟧*f⟦ocir⟧rm)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Oval</ets> + <ets>-form</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Having the form of an egg; having a figure such that any section in
the direction of the shorter diameter will be circular, and any in the
direction of the longer diameter will be oval.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ovally</ent>⟦br⟧
